title: Trump will not meet with Kim without seeing "concrete" action: WH
text:
Trump will not meet with Kim without seeing "concrete" action: WH 8:39pm GMT - 01:35 
U.S. President Donald Trump will not meet with North Korean leader Kim Jong-un unless he sees some ''concrete'' action by Pyongyang, the White House said on Friday. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
